    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been garage-kept and pampered since day one. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new, you've found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
